Vehicle Rental System
Problem Statement
Design a Vehicle Rental System that focuses only on Encapsulation and
Abstraction.
Requirements
1. Create an abstract class Vehicle:
○ Private fields:
■ vehicleNumber
■ vehicleType
○ Provide appropriate getter and setter methods.

2.Create a subclass Car:
● Private field:
○ dailyRate
● Implement calculateRentalCost(int days) to calculate:
days * dailyRate
3. Create a subclass Bike:
● Private field:
○ dailyRate
● Implement calculateRentalCost(int days) to calculate:
days * dailyRate
4. Create a subclass Truck:
● Private fields:
○ dailyRate
○ loadingCharge
● Implement calculateRentalCost(int days) as:
(days * dailyRate) + loadingCharge
5. All fields must be private and accessible only through getter and
setter methods.
6. In the main() method:

● Create one Car object.
● Create one Bike object.
● Create one Truck object.
● Display vehicle details and rental cost for a given number
of days.
